---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About" description="A bit about Jake.">
  <h1>About</h1>
  <p class="intro">
    I'm Jake. I made this site because I don't use social media but still want
    a way to let the people who care about me know what I'm up to.
  </p>

  <p>
    You'll find <a href="/updates">life updates</a> here whenever something
    worth sharing happens, the <a href="/projects">personal projects</a> I'm
    tinkering on, and <a href="/photos">photos</a> from trips and everyday
    moments.
  </p>

  <h2>Get in touch</h2>
  <p>
    The best way to reach me is email:
    <a href="mailto:hello@example.com">hello@example.com</a>.
  </p>
  <p class="muted">
    If you'd like to follow along without checking back, subscribe to the
    <a href="/updates/rss.xml">RSS feed</a> in your favorite reader.
  </p>
</Layout>
